<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>My Project Mail</title>
    <style type="text/css">
      body {
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
        min-height: 100%;
        font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;
        font-size: 16px;
        line-height: 1.5;
        background-color: #fafafa;
        color: #222222;
      }
      a {
        color: #000;
        text-decoration: none;
      }
      h1 {
        font-size: 24px;
        font-weight: 700;
        line-height: 1.5;
        margin-top: 0;
        margin-bottom: 15px;
        text-align: center;
      }
      p {
        margin-top: 0;
        margin-bottom: 24px;
      }
      table td {
        vertical-align: top;
      }
      .email-wrapper {
        max-width: 600px;
        margin: 0 auto;
      }
      .email-header {
        background-color: #dc3545;
        padding: 24px;
        color: #ffffff;
      }
      .email-body {
        padding: 24px;
        background-color: #ffffff;
      }
      .email-footer {
        background-color: #f6f6f6;
        padding: 24px;
      }
      .button {
        display: inline-block;
        background-color: #0070f3;
        color: #ffffff;
        font-size: 16px;
        font-weight: 700;
        text-align: center;
        text-decoration: none;
        padding: 12px 24px;
        border-radius: 4px;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="email-wrapper">
      <div class="email-header">
        <h1>Wellcome to My Project</h1>
      </div>
      <div class="email-body">
        <p>Hello <%= user.name %></p>
        <p>
          You are Requesting for reseting your password.To reset your password,
          please use the follwing link:
        </p>
        <h2><%= link %></h2>
        <p>
          Pleae click this link and the reset your password page within the next
          15 minutes.
        </p>
        <p>
          If you didn't request for Reseting your password on My Project. please
          ignore this email.
        </p>
        <div class="email-footer">
          <p>
            If you have any question, please don't hesitate to contact us at
            <a href="mailto:mail.com">abc@gamil.com</a>
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
